#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque PJMSNPCMP2 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$ON_BUDCOD
Return

$ON_OPPNUM
Return

$ON_PCCCOD
Return

$ON_XSL
Onevent INIT_AREA Call D_XSL(zc) From W4PJMSNPCMP2
Return

Subprog D_XSL(VALEUR)
Variable Clbfile VALEUR
If varinit([M]XSL,indice)=0
 Call INIXSL(VALEUR,"ANOMV") From INTRUTILA
Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

